.
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\forall f\left(x\right)\in\mathcal{C}\left[a,b\right]\quad\underset{h\left(a\right)=h\left(b\right)=0}{\underbrace{\forall h\left(x\right)\in\mathcal{\mathcal{C}}_{0}^{\infty}\left(a,b\right)}}\quad\int_{a}^{b}f\left(x\right)\cdot h\left(x\right)\mathrm{d}x=0\;\Rightarrow\;f\equiv0
\]

\end_inset


\emph on
Доказательство
\emph default
